{"word":"Dragon","slug":"dragon","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Dragon</b> A poisonous serpent<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=32&verse=33'>Deu 32:33</a><br/> A serpent of the desert<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=91&verse=13'>Psa 91:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=34&verse=13'>Isa 34:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=9&verse=11'>Jer 9:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=51&verse=37'>Jer 51:37</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=39&chapter=1&verse=3'>Mal 1:3</a><br/> A serpent of the sea<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=74&verse=13'>Psa 74:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=27&verse=1'>Isa 27:1</a><br/> A wolf<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=33&chapter=1&verse=8'>Mic 1:8</a><br/> Interpreted as a whale, in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=1&verse=21'>Gen 1:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=7&verse=12'>Job 7:12</a><br/> Serpent<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=7&verse=9'>Exo 7:9</a><br/> A term applied to Pharaoh<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=51&verse=9'>Isa 51:9</a><br/> A term applied to Satan<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=20&verse=2'>Rev 20:2</a><br/> Symbolic<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=29&verse=3'>Eze 29:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=32&verse=2'>Eze 32:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=12'>Rev 12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=16&verse=13'>Rev 16:13</a>"}]}